Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DEATH-DEFYING SAVIOR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who lured the Hero here!\NSo why am I left guarding the hostage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you like to be shattered?!\NHuh, little Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I don't need to kill you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You've only got until sundown anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there are guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get rid of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! So suddenly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban Style Sword Technique, {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Wave Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Baduck, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can destroy this Spire\Nand Popp destroys the Dark Ice Spire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Flazzard's Curse Field should disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to save you, Leona!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Spire's... still standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that?! Who interrupted us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What are these guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These monsters are different!\NWas this a trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Zaboera, Legion Commander of\Nthe Mystic Legion of the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is Mystban,\NLegion Commander of the Shadow Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mystic Legion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadow Legion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew you would split up\Nto come destroy the Spires.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the perfect opportunity\Nto wipe out you pesky gnats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Popp and Maam...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we've fallen into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Dai and Baduck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to worry about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So Dai is at the Dark Flame Spire.\NHow disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So be it. The Disciples of Aban\Nwill die out today either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll just enjoy\Ncrushing you worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This... This voice...\Nis one I'll never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, the Dark Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a Hero can handle\Nthis many enemies at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn to fear the Dark Army and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well! It's time for me to show off\Nthe Papunica Single-Blade Style once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Baduck, try to fight just the Mages!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out for their magic\Nand they're pretty weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... He's the one\Nwho killed Master Aban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But I didn't expect\Nthe Dark Commander himself to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd crush\Nall of you annoying creatures at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shut up! Don't assume everything's\Ngoing to go as planned, Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that little Mage\Nwho was there when I killed Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NI'm a student of Master Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How hilarious! No, how very pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The scrawny little student
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,desperately fought all this way\Nto avenge his master...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,only to end up dying a pitiful death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Screw you! I may die,\Nbut I won't go down without a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you feel even a fraction of\Nthe pain we felt when we lost our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We'll never forgive you\Nfor killing our kind Master Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a student of Master Aban, too!\NA Disciple of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have the wrong idea, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one who took Aban's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That primitive, ape-like emotion\Ncalled "kindness" was his undoing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Run Maam!\NHe's formidable at hand-to-hand, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's just too many of them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Aban...{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-He floats like a ghost,\Nbut he's so strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is he?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomakugutsosho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But this was Hyunckel's skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool. Hyunckel may have learned\Nhis sword skills from Aban,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but he learned how to control\NDark Aura from Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For controlling skeletons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Mystban\Nis the originator of that skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I can't move!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops! You aren't\Ngoing anywhere, you old goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I won't let\Nan old gremlin call me an old goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Having an old fossil like you\Nrunning around is even more annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let my words of death\Nlead you to an eternal slumber!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Zaraki!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is this creepy voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These are words of death\Ncalling to you from the netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When you succumb to them, your life ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now die, die, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}HYADARUKO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NICE-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit. Hadorra's spell\Nis even stronger than last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As a reward for killing Aban,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King Ban granted me a new body,\Nallowing me to power up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In combat, spells, and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I'm even stronger now\Nthan when I killed Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now you see that\Nyou have no hope for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Dai has already been pummeled\Nby the Mystic and Shadow Legions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and is dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't... We can't beat him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe if it was just Flazzard. But with\NHadorra and the other Legions here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You insects! For the crime of\Nstanding up against our great Dark Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,death is not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Begirama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste pain worse than death\Nfrom my inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right... I can't give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I give up,\Nwho's going to protect Maam?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn to ashes together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to protect Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go help Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give up! Not until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast Begirama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! That brat's spell\Noverpowered my own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra, are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance! They're disorganized!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I use?! Anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! Maam, did you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was amazing.\NI can't believe you cast Begirama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. I wasn't even thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to my mentor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just one day of training,\Nbut my attack spells increased in power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, Mentor!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Ice Spire can come later.\NLet's go help Dai and Baduck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.\NHow that snotty little brat has grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But now observe and know\Nthat there's always a bigger fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You recognize this spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done your Mage homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Begiragon!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the sound of Lord Hadorra\Nusing his most powerful spell, Begiragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra's here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Ice Spire is guarded by\NLord Hadorra himself and his minions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra is fighting Popp and Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Futile! Pure futility!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can break free from\NMystban's Tomakugutsosho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's see which of you dies first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Baduck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Curse you and your useless resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, we'll end it all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan, Baduck...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:17:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I have the strength\Nto defend both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear not! If we die, we die together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who was that?!\NWho dares to do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast King Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You! First you disappear\Nwithout a trace,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,then you show up and drop a boulder\Non us?! What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm helping the Disciples of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't just sit back\Nand let you ambush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you!\NTake care of that traitor first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of me? You're joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As if you small fry\Ncould defeat the Beast King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this giant monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You were alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see! I'm here to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Popp and Maam are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear not. A powerful ally\Nis headed for the Dark Ice Spire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's even more powerful than I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lord Hadorra, you're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They still remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I had to hold back to spare\Nthe Dark Ice Spire after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still breathing. I should\Nstrangle her to death just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You'll soon\Nsee each other in the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... I don't care\Nwhat happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just, please, let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the "kindness" you speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Not Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You're in love with this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing that,\NI can't possibly let her live now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You little maggot, you scarred my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now watch\Nas the girl you love dies horribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most fitting\Npunishment for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll impale her body\Non the top of the Dark Ice Spire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Ice Spire fell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Ice Spire...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So it really is Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Dai, I'll shatter\Nthe Dark Flame Spire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead to Valge Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go kick Flazzard's butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel... you're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.21,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:01.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one who saved Maam{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was Hyunckel, the Undead Legion Commander\Nwho vanished at the Underground Palace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra's anger explodes\Nat Hyunckel's betrayal of the Dark Army.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel seeks to avenge the death\Nof his father, Bartos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their incredible showdown begins at last.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.32,0:23:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Hyunckel Versus Hadorra"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:23:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
